  <brief_title>Effects of Preoperative Exercise in Gastric Cancer Patients With Metabolic Syndrome on Perioperative Outcome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Preoperative Exercise in Gastric Cancer Patients With Metabolic Syndrome on Perioperative Outcome: A Multicenter Prospective Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
