  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosed as gastric cancer by endoscopic biopsy

          -  Combined with metabolic syndrome

          -  Age limits from 18 to 80 years old

          -  American Society of Anesthesiologists physical status of Ⅱ or Ⅲ

          -  Scheduled for laparoscopic surgery

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiac or pulmonary disease

          -  The history of abdominal surgery

          -  The presence of gastrointestinal obstruction, perforation or necrosis;

          -  Radiographic evidence on distant metastasis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
